com.sebuilder.interpreter.factory

Class StepTypeFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sebuilder.interpreter.factory.StepTypeFactory

  • public class StepTypeFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory to create a StepType object from the step's name. Each step can be loaded from a settable primary package or a secondary package. Thanks to this mechanism, steps can be easily overridden when needed.
